Mr. Rangachari S Desikan, CEO - S Mobility

An Engineer and an alumni from the hallowed portals of IIM Ahemadabad, Mr. Desikan is true technocrat.

His international exposure with blue chip organizations, gives him a broader commercial overview and having served as the brand mentor for various companies at the apex level, he brings with him the astuteness and the sagacity of an experienced leader. Mr. Desikan has close to four decades of management experience, of which about twenty five years were at the helm of affairs.

He has been in corporate leadership roles with fortune five hundred companies like Rank Xerox and closer home, Modicorp amongst others. He has served at the highest levels as CFO, CEO and Director. Mr. T.M. Ramakrishnan, CEO - Devices Business


	Ramki is currently the Spearhead of S Mobility Ltd- Devices. He is responsible for the entire Operations and P&L of the business. His focus is to grow our presence in the retail counters thereby touching heights in terms of profitability, ASP, Volume, Revenue and Market Share. 

	 

	Ramki has over 17 years of work experience including his tenure with S Mobility Limited. He holds a vast experience in Telecom sector and prior to joining S Mobility he was associated with Videocon, MTS, Bharti Airtel and ITC. He has been delivering optimal results & business value in his career span by focusing on innovative marketing strategies and streamlining distribution by targeting the market potential & gaps in the system. 

	 

	He holds an Executive MBA degree from IIM, Bangalore. He is married to Ms. Deepa, a homemaker and they are blessed with two kids- Akash & Athira.  

	 

	You can reach him at tm.ramakrishnan@smobility.in. 
Mr. Saket Agarwal, CEO - Spice Digital

Saket Agarwal has been the driving force behind the current industry-leading position of Spice Digital Limited in the VAS arena. With his sharp business acumen, quiet leadership and people friendly attitude he orchestrates new partnerships with technology companies, content developers and aggregators, telecom operators, enterprise customers; develops business strategies and new business models to build social, profitable and ethical value based company and workforce.

Saket combines strict discipline of following processes with flexibility of individual contribution to deliver inspirational team work. He stays involved in product design lifecycle, bringing in rich experience and evolved perspective, motivating the teams to deliver path-breaking, robust, simple, revenue-enhancing, user-friendly products within framed timelines.

An Electronics Engineer and Physics Honours Master from BITS Pilani, Saket continued formal training with senior management programs from XLRI and IIM. He has looked into every aspect of the telecommunication industry, having a rich hands-on experience of 15+ years in this domain. As prior to joining SDL; he had been an integral part of the startup team at Spice Telecom Ltd. Punjab. He is also a qualified ISO auditor.

Saket is an ardent reader (recommends "The Alchemist" and "The Google Story" to one and all), passionate about sports and enjoys traveling. His mantra for success is "To ensure you commit what you can deliver and deliver what you committed". Mr. Subramanian Murali, CFO

Over 25 years of professional experience. Is a business transformation and startup specialist, amply demonstrated during his 21 year stint at HCL
