Mr. A.Sridhar, Head Service

Sridhar is responsible for entire Service gamut. His role is to strategize, design, build and continuously improve Devices Service Delivery mechanism for S Mobility operations and ensuring service as differentiator for SPICE. .


	Backed with over 20  years of varied  experience, Sridhar  has handled  multiple roles including Customer Service, Technical Support, Product Sales and Solution Sales. He joins us from Sterlite. Before this, he  had worked in HCL InfoSystems for 20 years. 
	 


		He holds a MBA degree through DLP after a Diploma Engineering - ECE. He is married to Mrs. M. Ambigavady, a home maker and blessed with  two children S. Ajay and S. Akash. He enjoys travelling and  book reading  of various genres.

		 

		 


	 
Mr. Divya Gupta, National Sales Head

Divya is currently leading the Sales Operations PAN India of S Mobility. He is responsible for sales, revenue generation, distribution and organized trade business. Divya has over 15 years of work experience including his tenure with S Mobility Limited.

He holds a vast experience in Telecom sector and prior to joining S Mobility he was associated with MTS, Reliance Big TV and Bharti Airtel. He holds a PGD in Business Management from Bhartiya Vidhya Bhawan, Jaipur. He is married to Ms. Vineeta, an entreprenuer working for educational technologies and they are blessed with a son- Vibhor. 

	 

	You can reach him at divya.gupta@smobility.in
Mr. Amandeep Singh, CFO – Devices Business

Amandeep is currently looking after the Finance & Accounts operations. He has been instrumental in implementing SAP where he was involved right from designing & defining the framework & process flows till the implementation. He also played a crucial role in cluster formation and was key member in stabilizing the clusters.

	 

	Amandeep has over 13 years of work experience including his tenure with S Mobility Limited. Before joining S Mobility he was associated with companies like Praveen Kumar Singhal, Ashish & Company, Harinder Industries (Tenac). He has been instrumental in determining & analyzing root cause for problems & taking corrective measures. He has a vast knowledge of operations management including financial & performance reports, MIS, budgeting, capital expenditure, etc.

	 

	He is a CA and holds a Bachelors degree in Commerce (Hons). He is married to Ms. Amanpreet Kaur, and they are blessed with twin kids- Jasleen and Jasmine. 

	 

	You can reach him at amandeep.singh@smobility.in
Krishna Kumar, CEO – Retail Business   

Krishna is a thoroughbred retail professional with over 21 years of Retail experience, 13 years in the Middle East and remaining in India. He has been a part of Spice Family since 2004 and one of the few members of the retail business who has been with the vertical since its inception. He has worked with multi nationals like Jumbo Electronics & Al Futtaim Group in Dubai setting up and running large format retail stores.  



 






